440993_448764600266031528_o-1.jpg 2040w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/27164151_158768851440993_448764600266031528_o-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/27164151_158768851440993_448764600266031528_o-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/27164151_158768851440993_448764600266031528_o-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/27164151_158768851440993_448764600266031528_o-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\\\" sizes=\\\"auto, (max-width: 2040px) 100vw, 2040px\\\" width=\\\"2040\\\" height=\\\"1530\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" decoding=\\\"async\\\"><\\/p><div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;padding-bottom:1.5em;padding-top:1.5em;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><figure class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;display:block;margin:0px auto 2em;max-width:100%;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_417\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-417\\\"><figcaption class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);box-sizing:border-box;display:block;font-size:0.9em;padding:0.4em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-417\\\"><i>C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf<\\/i><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><strong>Gi\\u1ea3m h\\u1ecda ti\\u1ebft tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ed3 n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian r\\u1ed9ng l\\u1edbn, vi\\u1ec7c trang tr\\u00ed v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c gam m\\u00e0u \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 l\\u00f4i cu\\u1ed1n. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, khi \\u0111\\u1ed1i di\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian nh\\u1ecf h\\u1eb9p, vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0m c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ed1i, g\\u00e2y s\\u1ef1 l\\u1ed9n x\\u1ed9n v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m t\\u0103ng c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c ch\\u1eadt ch\\u1ed9i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3, ch\\u00fang ta n\\u00ean l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt c\\u00f3 gam m\\u00e0u nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng nh\\u01b0 pastel, be, ho\\u1eb7c tr\\u1eafng. S\\u1ef1 t\\u1ed1i gi\\u1ea3n n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 gi\\u00fap c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean sang tr\\u1ecdng v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u01a1n m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian t\\u01b0\\u01a1i s\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 m\\u1edf r\\u1ed9ng h\\u01a1n. Ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt c\\u00f3 b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t tr\\u01a1n l\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 \\u00edt h\\u1ecda ti\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u1ed1t \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m cho c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd v\\u00e0 thu h\\u00fat \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><strong>C\\u00e1ch trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Khi \\u0111\\u1ec1 c\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf, ch\\u00fang ta s\\u1ebd g\\u1eb7p nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch kh\\u00e1c nhau. T\\u00f9y thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch, ch\\u00fang ta s\\u1ebd \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1ch trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u1ed1 Tr\\u00ed Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd 9m2:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd c\\u00f3 di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch 9m2, vi\\u1ec7c b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n v\\u00e0 g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft. B\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ec9 n\\u00ean c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0 gi\\u01b0\\u1eddng g\\u1ea5p, m\\u1ed9t b\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t gh\\u1ebf, m\\u1ed9t t\\u1ee7 qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o nh\\u1ecf, m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ebfp ga mini v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee5 b\\u1ebfp thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu. S\\u01a1n t\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c gam m\\u00e0u s\\u00e1ng s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i h\\u01a1n. B\\u1ed5 sung m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1edf ra.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u1ed1 Tr\\u00ed Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd 12m2:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd v\\u1edbi di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch 12m2 c\\u0169ng tu\\u00e2n theo ti\\u00eau ch\\u00ed c\\u1ee7a ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd 9m2. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ed5 sung m\\u1ed9t k\\u1ec7 s\\u00e1ch nh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ec3 trang tr\\u00ed v\\u00e0 l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef s\\u00e1ch v\\u1edf ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u1ed1 Tr\\u00ed Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd 15m2:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch 15m2, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 th\\u00eam c\\u00e1c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 trang tr\\u00ed nh\\u01b0 gi\\u1ea5y d\\u00e1n t\\u01b0\\u1eddng ho\\u1eb7c tr\\u1ea3i s\\u00e0n g\\u1ed7 \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng gian sang tr\\u1ecdng h\\u01a1n. B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 trang tr\\u00ed b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u00e8n nh\\u1ea5p nh\\u00e1y v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e1c ch\\u1eadu c\\u00e2y nh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i m\\u00e0u xanh v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c t\\u01b0\\u01a1i m\\u00e1t cho ph\\u00f2ng.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Appl