m\\u00e1i v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n nghi. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u c\\u1ea7n l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi t\\u00ecm ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf cho m\\u1ed9t ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u1edf:<\\/span><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.25em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">C\\u1ea3nh gi\\u00e1c khi \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u1ecdc ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h3><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\"><div class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">R\\u1ee7i ro l\\u1eeba \\u0111\\u1ea3o ti\\u1ec1n c\\u1ecdc khi thu\\u00ea nh\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb, nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t m\\u00e1nh kh\\u00f3e m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng \\u00edt ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tr\\u1ebb non d\\u1ea1, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng ai thi\\u1ebfu kinh nghi\\u1ec7m, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb m\\u1eafc v\\u00e0o.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">K\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt l\\u1eeba \\u0111\\u1ea3o trong vi\\u1ec7c thu\\u00ea ph\\u00f2ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng bi\\u1ebfn th\\u1ec3, nh\\u01b0ng k\\u1ecbch b\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 k\\u1ebb gian gi\\u1ea3 danh ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 ho\\u1eb7c trung gian, \\u0111\\u01b0a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi thu\\u00ea \\u0111i xem nh\\u1eefng c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng v\\u1edbi v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i r\\u1ea5t h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn v\\u00e0 sau \\u0111\\u00f3 g\\u1ea5p g\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u00f2i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi thu\\u00ea \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ecb \\u201cm\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ed7\\u201d. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m m\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tr\\u1ebb, ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ee7 c\\u1ea3nh gi\\u00e1c, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng b\\u1ecb m\\u1ea5t ti\\u1ec1n c\\u1ecdc m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch kh\\u00f4ng ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ec3 ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u00e1nh nh\\u1eefng r\\u1ee7i ro n\\u00e0y, quan tr\\u1ecdng nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng n\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u1ecdc tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi ki\\u1ec3m tra k\\u1ef9 ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd. N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 xem x\\u00e9t v\\u00e0 quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh s\\u1eb5n l\\u00f2ng \\u0111\\u01b0a ti\\u1ec1n c\\u1ecdc, h\\u00e3y y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 cung c\\u1ea5p m\\u1ed9t H\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u1ecdc ho\\u1eb7c m\\u1ed9t Gi\\u1ea5y bi\\u00ean nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u00e3 ghi nh\\u1eadn vi\\u1ec7c nh\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec1n c\\u1ecdc.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 quy\\u1ec1n l\\u1ee3i c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0 tr\\u00e1nh xa kh\\u1ecfi nh\\u1eefng k\\u1ebb gian l\\u1eeba \\u0111\\u1ea3o. \\u0110\\u1eebng bao gi\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea3n d\\u1ea1ng ho\\u1ea3ng s\\u1ee3 ho\\u1eb7c \\u00e1p l\\u1ef1c t\\u1eeb b\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i l\\u00e0m m\