(563, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Sinh vi\\u00ean \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd c\\u1ea7n nh\\u1eefng g\\u00ec? Danh s\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"sinh-vien-o-tro-can-nhung-gi-danh-sach-nhung-vat-dung-thiet-yeu-khi-o-tro\",\"slug_id\":\"23\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0o cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9c l\\u1eadp \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd, sinh vi\\u00ean c\\u1ea7n chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y su\\u00f4n s\\u1ebb v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t danh s\\u00e1ch c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00e0 sinh vi\\u00ean n\\u00ean c\\u00f3 khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<header class=\\\"entry-header\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);display:block;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><div class=\\\"entry-image relative\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;position:relative !important;\\\"><a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 44, 119);text-decoration:none;touch-action:manipulation;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/danh-sach-nhung-vat-dung-thiet-yeu-khi-o-tro\\/\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\\\" style=\\\"aspect-ratio:960\\/720;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;height:auto;max-width:100%;opacity:1;transition:opacity 1s;vertical-align:middle;width:840px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/52013870_317406932243850_7229320778334863360_n.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd t\\u1ea1i h\\u00f2a l\\u1ea1c, nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd h\\u00f2a l\\u1ea1c, ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd minh ch\\u00e2u\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/52013870_317406932243850_7229320778334863360_n.jpg 960w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/52013870_317406932243850_7229320778334863360_n-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/52013870_317406932243850_7229320778334863360_n-768x576.jpg 768w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\\\" width=\\\"960\\\" height=\\\"720\\\" decoding=\\\"async\\\" fetchpriority=\\\"high\\\"><\\/a><\\/div><\\/header><div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;padding-bottom:1.5em;padding-top:1.5em;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Khi b\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0o cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9c l\\u1eadp \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd, sinh vi\\u00ean c\\u1ea7n chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y su\\u00f4n s\\u1ebb v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t danh s\\u00e1ch c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00e0 sinh vi\\u00ean n\\u00ean c\\u00f3 khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd:<\\/p><div class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:20.16px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">\\u1ed4 Kh\\u00f3a Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\">D\\u00f9 b\\u1ea1n \\u1edf nh\\u00e0 hay \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd, an ninh lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 quan tr\\u1ecdng m\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ec1 cao. Ngay sau khi b\\u1ea1n nh\\u1eadn ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd t\\u1eeb ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0, vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean n\\u00ean l\\u00e0m l\\u00e0 thay th\\u1ebf \\u1ed5 kh\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an to\\u00e0n cho b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n v\\u00e0 t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi tr\\u00e1nh nguy c\\u01a1 b\\u1ecb x\\u00e2m ph\\u1ea1m quy\\u1ec1n ri\\u00eang t\\u01b0. V\\u1edbi \\u1ed5 kh\\u00f3a c\\u00f3 s\\u1eb5n t\\u1ea1i ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ecdn c\\u00e1ch tr\\u1ea3 ngay cho ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 ho\\u1eb7c t\\u1ea1m gi\\u1eef l\\u1ea1i cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi b\\u1ea1n r\\u1eddi \\u0111i v\\u00e0 b\\u00e0n giao l\\u1ea1i cho ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn \\u1ed5 kh\\u00f3a kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n l\\u00e0 v\\u1ec1 gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ea3, m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng. Kh\\u00f4ng n\\u00ean ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m khi mua \\u1ed5 kh\\u00f3a, h\\u00e3y ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eefng lo\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an to\\u00e0n t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a v\\u00e0 tr\\u00e1nh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nguy c\\u01a1 b\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u00e1nh c\\u1eafp.<\\/div><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;\\\"><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.25em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">Ch\\u0103n, Ga, G\\u1ed1i, \\u0110\\u1ec7m<\\/strong><\\/h3><div class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\">M\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ec1u hi\\u1ec3u r\\u1eb1ng gi\\u1ea5c ng\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 quan tr\\u1ecdng trong vi\\u1ec7c duy tr\\u00ec s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3. Khi s\\u1ed1ng \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd, xa nh\\u00e0, vi\\u1ec7c t\\u1ef1 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n t\\u1eeb vi\\u1ec7c \\u0103n u\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn gi\\u1ea5c ng\\u1ee7 tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 quan tr\\u1ecdng. \\u0110\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o gi\\u1ea5c ng\\u1ee7 c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3, h\\u00e3y chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb cho m\\u00ecnh m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ed9 ch\\u0103n, ga, g\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ec7m (ho\\u1eb7c n\\u1ec7m) ri\\u00eang bi\\u1ec7t. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1ea5c ng\\u1ee7 s\\u00e2u, tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i nh\\u1ea5t, gi\\u00fap c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u1ed7i ng\\u00e0y.<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><p><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-809 image_resized\\\" style=\\\"aspect-ratio:900\\/1125;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;height:auto;max-width:100%;opacity:1;transition:opacity 1s;vertical-align:middle;width:900px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/04\\/phong-tro-co-gac-lung.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Danh s\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/04\\/phong-tro-co-gac-lung.jpg 900w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/04\\/phong-tro-co-gac-lung-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/04\\/phong-tro-co-gac-lung-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/04\\/phong-tro-co-gac-lung-768x960.jpg 768w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\\\" width=\\\"900\\\" height=\\\"1125\\\" decoding=\\\"async\\\"><\\/p><div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;padding-bottom:1.5em;padding-top:1.5em;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><div><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\"><figure class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;clear:both;display:block;margin:0px auto 2em;max-width:100%;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_809\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"caption-attachment-809\\\"><figcaption class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);box-sizing:border-box;display:block;font-size:0.9em;padding:0.4em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-809\\\"><i>Danh s\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd<\\/i><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><\\/div><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.25em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">T\\u1ee7 Qu\\u1ea7n \\u00c1o, M\\u00f3c Treo Qu\\u1ea7n \\u00c1o<\\/strong><\\/h3><div class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\">T\\u1ee7 qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o, gi\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u1ee1 v\\u00e0 m\\u00f3c treo l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 thi\\u1ebfu trong cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi. N\\u1ebfu kh\\u00f4ng gian trong ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u1ee7 r\\u1ed9ng, vi\\u1ec7c mua m\\u1ed9t t\\u1ee7 qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i trong vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eafp x\\u1ebfp trang ph\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ee5 ki\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh. B\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i t\\u1ee7 gh\\u00e9p c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 th\\u00e1o l\\u1eafp d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng m\\u1ed7i khi b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea7n di chuy\\u1ec3n ho\\u1eb7c chuy\\u1ec3n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd. Trong tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p kh\\u00f4ng gian trong ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf, vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng gi\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u1ee1 treo qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3.<\\/div><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.25em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u00e0n H\\u1ecdc, Gi\\u00e1 S\\u00e1ch<\\/strong><\\/h3><div class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;\\\">H\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp l\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecdng tr\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a sinh vi\\u00ean, do \\u0111\\u00f3, h\\u00e3y \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb m\\u1ed9t g\\u00f3c h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 cho b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n. B\\u00e0n h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 gi\\u00e1\\/k\\u1ec7 s\\u00e1ch l\\u00e0 hai m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 thi\\u1ebfu khi b\\u1ea1n \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd. T\\u00f9y thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng gian c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn mua m\\u1ed9t b\\u00e0n h\\u1ecdc c\\u00f3 k\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i nh\\u01b0 \\u1edf nh\\u00e0 ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u00e0n mini, b\\u00e0n g\\u1ea5p ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;\\\">Gi\\u00e1 s\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c k\\u1ec7 s\\u00e1ch l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c s\\u00e1ch v\\u1edf m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m th\\u1eddi gian m\\u1ed7i khi c\\u1ea7n t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n duy tr\\u00ec m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd v\\u00e0 g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng, t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i cho vi\\u1ec7c t\\u1eadp trung v\\u00e0 h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 h\\u01a1n.<\\/p><\\/div><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;\\\"><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.25em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">Qu\\u1ea1t \\u0110i\\u1ec7n<\\/strong><\\/h3><div class=\\\"p\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\">Vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc qu\\u1ea1t \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh \\u0111i\\u1ec1u kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 thi\\u1ebfu trong nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y n\\u1eafng n\\u00f3ng. T\\u00f9y thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh, m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 sinh vi\\u00ean c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ecdn l\\u1ef1a vi\\u1ec7c l\\u1eafp \\u0111\\u1eb7t m\\u00e1y \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u00f2a ho\\u1eb7c m\\u00e1y l\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u00e1t m\\u1ebb v\\u00e0 tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, \\u0111a s\\u1ed1 sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u1eabn \\u01b0a chu\\u1ed9ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng qu\\u1ea1t \\u0111i\\u1ec7n v\\u00ec gi\\u00e1 th\\u00e0nh th\\u1ea5p h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0 t\\u00ednh ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i khi c\\u1ea7n chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ebfn ch\\u1ed7 \\u1edf m\\u1edbi.<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><p><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-573 image_resized\\\" style=\\\"aspect-ratio:799\\/603;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;height:auto;max-width:100%;opacity:1;transition:opacity 1s;vertical-align:middle;width:799px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/Nhung-dieu-can-luu-y-khi-ky-hop-dong-thue-phong-tro-dep.png\\\" alt=\\\"Danh s\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu khi \\u1edf tr\\u1ecd\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/Nhung-dieu-can-luu-y-khi-ky-hop-dong-thue-phong-tro-dep.png 799w, https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/Nhung-dieu-can-luu-y-