lign:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"23:1-23:40\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">4. G\\u1eb7p g\\u1ee1 v\\u00e0 tr\\u00f2 chuy\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2><ul style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;padding:0px;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"25:1-28:0\\\"><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0.6em;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"25:1-25:120\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">Quan s\\u00e1t th\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ed9, c\\u00e1ch c\\u01b0 x\\u1eed c\\u1ee7a ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0:<\\/strong>&nbsp;Ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ec7n, nhi\\u1ec7t t\\u00ecnh, s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u00e1p th\\u1eafc m\\u1eafc hay kh\\u00f4ng?<\\/span><\\/p><\\/li><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0.6em;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"26:1-26:126\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">H\\u1ecfi k\\u1ef9 v\\u1ec1 h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng thu\\u00ea nh\\u00e0:<\\/strong>&nbsp;C\\u00e1c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u kho\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 an ninh, tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m c\\u1ee7a ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 v\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi thu\\u00ea \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o?<\\/span><\\/p><\\/li><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0.6em;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"27:1-28:0\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">Y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e0 cung c\\u1ea5p th\\u00f4ng tin li\\u00ean l\\u1ea1c c\\u1e