\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);box-sizing:border-box;display:block;font-size:0.9em;padding:0.4em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-488\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><i>C\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 t\\u00ednh \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u00e0 an ninh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t khu v\\u1ef1c tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh thu\\u00ea nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd<\\/i><\\/span><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"29:1-29:39\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">5. Tin t\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0o tr\\u1ef1c gi\\u00e1c c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2><ul style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;list-style:disc;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;padding:0px;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"31:1-33:0\\\"><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0.6em;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"31:1-31:117\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">Sau khi thu th\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 th\\u00f4ng tin, h\\u00e3y d\\u00e0nh th\\u1eddi gian suy ngh\\u0129 v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/li><li style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0.6em;\\\" data-sourcepos=\\\"32:1-33:0\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y kh\\u00f4