i\\u00e1c v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ec1 cao \\u00fd th\\u1ee9c an to\\u00e0n:<\\/strong>&nbsp;D\\u00f9 b\\u1ea1n thu\\u00ea nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd \\u1edf khu v\\u1ef1c an ninh t\\u1ed1t \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u00e2u, b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng n\\u00ean c\\u1ea9n th\\u1eadn, \\u0111\\u1ec1 ph\\u00f2ng k\\u1ebb gian.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">Vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 t\\u00ednh \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u00e0 an ninh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t khu v\\u1ef1c tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh thu\\u00ea nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t b\\u01b0\\u1edbc quan tr\\u1ecdng gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ef1 an to\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea1nh ph\\u00fac khi s\\u1ed1ng trong m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng m\\u1edbi. \\u0110\\u1eebng ng\\u1ea7n ng\\u1ea1i chi ti\\u1ebft v\\u00e0 c\\u00e2n nh\\u1eafc k\\u1ef9 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi ra quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh cu\\u1ed1i c\\u00f9ng.<\\/span><\\/p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family:system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;text-rendering:optimizespeed;width:840px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;\\\">Nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd Minh Ch\\u00e2u, ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd H\\u00f2a L\\u1ea1c<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\">Ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd\\/chung c\\u01b0 mini cao c\\u1ea5p Minh Ch\\u00e2u t\\u1ea1i Khu c\\u00f4