(708, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"cac-luu-y-khi-trang-tri-phong-tro-nho\",\"slug_id\":\"18\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Trang tr\\u00ed m\\u1ed9t c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t th\\u00e1ch th\\u1ee9c, nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t v\\u00e0i b\\u00ed quy\\u1ebft th\\u00f4ng minh, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1eb9p m\\u1eaft, tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n nghi. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng l\\u01b0u \\u00fd quan tr\\u1ecdng khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf m\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n n\\u00ean xem x\\u00e9t:\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trang tr\\u00ed m\\u1ed9t c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t th\\u00e1ch th\\u1ee9c, nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t v\\u00e0i b\\u00ed quy\\u1ebft th\\u00f4ng minh, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1eb9p m\\u1eaft, tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec7n nghi. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng l\\u01b0u \\u00fd quan tr\\u1ecdng khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf m\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n n\\u00ean xem x\\u00e9t:<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>T\\u00ednh to\\u00e1n ch\\u00ednh x\\u00e1c c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng trong ph\\u00f2ng<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf, vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u01b0a ra c\\u00e1c quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh th\\u00f4ng minh v\\u1ec1 b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 r\\u1ea5t quan tr\\u1ecdng. Qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ed3 n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t trong kh\\u00f4ng gian nh\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m cho c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean ch\\u1eadt ch\\u1ed9i v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u1edf. Thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3, t\\u1ed1i gi\\u1ea3n h\\u00f3a vi\\u1ec7c ch\\u1ecdn l\\u1ef1a n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 t\\u1eadp trung v\\u00e0o nh\\u1eefng m\\u00f3n \\u0111\\u1ed3 thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfn l\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u00f4ng minh.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">H\\u00e3y ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eefng m\\u00f3n \\u0111\\u1ed3 n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 \\u00edch cho cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n. Tr\\u00e1nh b\\u00e0y tr\\u00ed qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u t\\u1ee7 k\\u1ec7 hay \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft, nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 gi\\u00fap c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng h\\u01a1n m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian s\\u1ed1ng ti\\u1ec7n nghi v\\u00e0 tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i h\\u01a1n.<\\/p><\\/div><figure class=\\\"image image_resized\\\" style=\\\"height:auto;width:1024px;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-649 image_resized\\\" style=\\\"aspect-ratio:1024\\/480;border-style:none;max-width:100%;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/02\\/9a46cf8f-e64d-4544-8117-3275d8d15f75_cover.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf\\\" width=\\\"1024\\\" height=\\\"480\\\"><\\/figure><div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><figure class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"margin:0px auto 2em;max-width:100%;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_649\\\"><figcaption class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);font-size:0.9em;padding:0.4em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-649\\\"><i>C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf<\\/i><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>L\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111a n\\u0103ng<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong kh\\u00f4ng gian nh\\u1ecf c\\u1ee7a ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd, vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111a n\\u0103ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p th\\u00f4ng minh v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m kh\\u00f4ng gian. Nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111a n\\u0103ng n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 gi\\u00fap t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u h\\u00f3a di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i trong vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 \\u0111i\\u1ec3n h\\u00ecnh c\\u1ee7a v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111a n\\u0103ng bao g\\u1ed3m b\\u00e0n g\\u1ea5p c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp ho\\u1eb7c l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c trong su\\u1ed1t ng\\u00e0y, v\\u00e0 sau \\u0111\\u00f3 chuy\\u1ec3n sang ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng l\\u00e0m b\\u00e0n \\u0103n khi c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft. N\\u1ed3i n\\u1ea5u c\\u01a1m \\u0111a c\\u00f4ng n\\u0103ng c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn th\\u00f4ng minh \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1edbt s\\u1ed1 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u1ed3i ch\\u1ea3o trong nh\\u00e0, ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m kh\\u00f4ng gian l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi cung c\\u1ea5p nhi\\u1ec1u t\\u00f9y ch\\u1ecdn n\\u1ea5u \\u0103n.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">N\\u1ec7m g\\u1ea5p l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ti\\u1ec7n l\\u1ee3i \\u0111\\u1ec3 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m kh\\u00f4ng gian sau khi d\\u00f9ng xong. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, gh\\u1ebf sofa d\\u1ea1ng g\\u1ea5p c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng l\\u00e0m gi\\u01b0\\u1eddng ng\\u1ee7 khi c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft, gi\\u00fap ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch v\\u00e0 t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian \\u0111a n\\u0103ng linh ho\\u1ea1t trong ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>T\\u1eadn d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a kh\\u00f4ng gian<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Kho\\u1ea3ng tr\\u1ed1ng m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng gian tr\\u1ed1ng trong ph\\u00f2ng c\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1eadn d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a. D\\u01b0\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c kh\\u00f4ng gian sau c\\u00e1nh c\\u1eeda, ch\\u00fang ta c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00f3c treo \\u0111\\u1ec3 treo n\\u00f3n, m\\u0169 ho\\u1eb7c \\u00e1o kho\\u00e1c, gi\\u00fap ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m kh\\u00f4ng gian l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">N\\u1ebfu ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd c\\u00f3 g\\u00e1c l\\u1eedng, ch\\u00fang ta c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng g\\u00f3c d\\u01b0\\u1edbi c\\u1ea7u thang \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1eb7t m\\u1ed9t t\\u1ee7 nh\\u1ecf, t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef th\\u00eam. Tr\\u00ean t\\u01b0\\u1eddng cao, c\\u00e1c k\\u1ec7 treo c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eafp x\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ef1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3 trang tr\\u00ed, t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 t\\u1eadn d\\u1ee5ng kh\\u00f4ng gian kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00f3.<\\/p><\\/div><figure class=\\\"image image_resized\\\" style=\\\"height:auto;width:799px;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-573 image_resized\\\" style=\\\"aspect-ratio:799\\/603;border-style:none;max-width:100%;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/Nhung-dieu-can-luu-y-khi-ky-hop-dong-thue-phong-tro-dep.png\\\" alt=\\\"C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf\\\" width=\\\"799\\\" height=\\\"603\\\"><\\/figure><div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><figure class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"margin:0px auto 2em;max-width:100%;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_573\\\"><figcaption class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);font-size:0.9em;padding:0.4em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-573\\\"><i>C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf<\\/i><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>B\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd, g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng nh\\u1ecf, kh\\u00f4ng n\\u00ean qu\\u00e1 t\\u1ea3i kh\\u00f4ng gian b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c. Thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3, b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea7n th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ed1i s\\u1ed1ng g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 ng\\u0103n n\\u1eafp.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">H\\u00e3y \\u0111\\u1eb7t nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u sau khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, tr\\u00e1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c r\\u1ea3i r\\u00e1c trong ph\\u00f2ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o r\\u1eb1ng kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 r\\u00e1c th\\u1ea3i n\\u00e0o b\\u1ecb b\\u1ecf b\\u1eeba b\\u00e3i. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd v\\u00e0 g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng h\\u01a1n. \\u0110\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u00e9n \\u0111\\u0129a b\\u1eeba b\\u00e3i sau khi d\\u00f9ng xong, h\\u00e3y d\\u1ecdn d\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 r\\u1eeda ch\\u00fang ngay sau b\\u1eefa \\u0103n.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Ngo\\u00e0i ra, h\\u00e3y h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf vi\\u1ec7c mua qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ed3 trang tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u00e1nh l\\u00e0m cho kh\\u00f4ng gian tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean qu\\u00e1 t\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0m cho ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean r\\u1ed1i m\\u1eaft m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i cho b\\u1ee5i b\\u1ea9n t\\u00edch t\\u1ee5.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>T\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u chi ph\\u00ed b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3 second hand<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng nh\\u1ecf, kh\\u00f4ng n\\u00ean qu\\u00e1 t\\u1ea3i kh\\u00f4ng gian b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c. Thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3, b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ea7n th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ed1i s\\u1ed1ng g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 ng\\u0103n n\\u1eafp.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">H\\u00e3y \\u0111\\u1eb7t nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u sau khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, tr\\u00e1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c r\\u1ea3i r\\u00e1c trong ph\\u00f2ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o r\\u1eb1ng kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 r\\u00e1c th\\u1ea3i n\\u00e0o b\\u1ecb b\\u1ecf b\\u1eeba b\\u00e3i. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd v\\u00e0 g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng h\\u01a1n. \\u0110\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u00e9n \\u0111\\u0129a b\\u1eeba b\\u00e3i sau khi d\\u00f9ng xong, h\\u00e3y d\\u1ecdn d\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 r\\u1eeda ch\\u00fang ngay sau b\\u1eefa \\u0103n.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Ngo\\u00e0i ra, h\\u00e3y h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf vi\\u1ec7c mua qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ed3 trang tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u00e1nh l\\u00e0m cho kh\\u00f4ng gian tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean qu\\u00e1 t\\u1ea3i v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0m cho ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean r\\u1ed1i m\\u1eaft m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i cho b\\u1ee5i b\\u1ea9n t\\u00edch t\\u1ee5.<\\/p><\\/div><figure class=\\\"image image_resized\\\" style=\\\"height:auto;width:2040px;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-417 image_resized\\\" style=\\\"aspect-ratio:1200\\/1200;border-style:none;max-width:100%;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/nhatrominhchau.info\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/10\\/27164151_158768851440993_448764600266031528_o-1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf\\\" width=\\\"1200\\\" height=\\\"1200\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\"><\\/figure><div class=\\\"entry-content single-page\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:medium;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><figure class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"margin:0px auto 2em;max-width:100%;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_417\\\"><figcaption class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);font-size:0.9em;padding:0.4em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-417\\\"><i>C\\u00e1c l\\u01b0u \\u00fd khi trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf<\\/i><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>Gi\\u1ea3m h\\u1ecda ti\\u1ebft tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ed3 n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian r\\u1ed9ng l\\u1edbn, vi\\u1ec7c trang tr\\u00ed v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c gam m\\u00e0u \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 l\\u00f4i cu\\u1ed1n. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, khi \\u0111\\u1ed1i di\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian nh\\u1ecf h\\u1eb9p, vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0m c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ed1i, g\\u00e2y s\\u1ef1 l\\u1ed9n x\\u1ed9n v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m t\\u0103ng c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c ch\\u1eadt ch\\u1ed9i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Thay v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u00f3, ch\\u00fang ta n\\u00ean l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt c\\u00f3 gam m\\u00e0u nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng nh\\u01b0 pastel, be, ho\\u1eb7c tr\\u1eafng. S\\u1ef1 t\\u1ed1i gi\\u1ea3n n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 gi\\u00fap c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean sang tr\\u1ecdng v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u01a1n m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n t\\u1ea1o ra m\\u1ed9t kh\\u00f4ng gian t\\u01b0\\u01a1i s\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 m\\u1edf r\\u1ed9ng h\\u01a1n. Ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed3 v\\u1eadt c\\u00f3 b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t tr\\u01a1n l\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 \\u00edt h\\u1ecda ti\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u1ed1t \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m cho c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd v\\u00e0 thu h\\u00fat \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong>C\\u00e1ch trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch kh\\u00e1c nhau<\\/strong><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Khi \\u0111\\u1ec1 c\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd nh\\u1ecf, ch\\u00fang ta s\\u1ebd g\\u1eb7p nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch kh\\u00e1c nhau. T\\u00f9y thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch, ch\\u00fang ta s\\u1ebd \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1ch trang tr\\u00ed ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u1ed1 Tr\\u00ed Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd 9m2:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd c\\u00f3 di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch 9m2, vi\\u1ec7c b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n v\\u00e0 g\\u1ecdn g\\u00e0ng l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft. B\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ec9 n\\u00ean c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadt d\\u1ee5ng c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0 gi\\u01b0\\u1eddng g\\u1ea5p, m\\u1ed9t b\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t gh\\u1ebf, m\\u1ed9t t\\u1ee7 qu\\u1ea7n \\u00e1o nh\\u1ecf, m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ebfp ga mini v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee5 b\\u1ebfp thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu. S\\u01a1n t\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c gam m\\u00e0u s\\u00e1ng s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i h\\u01a1n. B\\u1ed5 sung m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1edf ra.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u1ed1 Tr\\u00ed Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd 12m2:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd v\\u1edbi di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch 12m2 c\\u0169ng tu\\u00e2n theo ti\\u00eau ch\\u00ed c\\u1ee7a ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd 9m2. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ed5 sung m\\u1ed9t k\\u1ec7 s\\u00e1ch nh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ec3 trang tr\\u00ed v\\u00e0 l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef s\\u00e1ch v\\u1edf ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0111\\u1ea1c.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\"><strong style=\\\"font-weight:bolder;\\\">B\\u1ed1 Tr\\u00ed Ph\\u00f2ng Tr\\u1ecd 15m2:<\\/strong><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1.3em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;\\\">Trong c\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi di\\u1ec7n t\\u00edch 15m2, b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 th\\u00eam c\\u00e1c y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 trang tr\\u00ed nh\\u01b0 gi\\u1ea5y d\\u00e1n t\\u01b0\\u1eddng ho\\u1eb7c tr\\u1ea3i s\\u00e0n g\\u1ed7 \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o n\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng gian sang tr\\u1ecdng h\\u01a1n. B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 trang tr\\u00ed b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u00e8n nh\\u1ea5p nh\\u00e1y v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e1c ch\\u1eadu c\\u00e2y nh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i m\\u00e0u xanh v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c t\\u01b0\\u01a1i m\\u00e1t cho ph\\u00f2ng.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"color:rgb(10,10,10);font-family:\'system-ui\', \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\';font-size:1.6em;font-style:normal;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0px;text-align:justify;width:840px;\\\"><strong style=\\\"font-weight:bolder;\\\">Nh\\u00e0 tr\\u1ecd Minh Ch\\u00e2u, ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd H\\u00f2a L\\u1ea1c<\\/strong><\\/h2><div style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><div>Ph\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ecd\\/chung c\\u01b0 mini cao c\\u1ea5p Minh Ch\\u00e2u t\\u1ea1i Khu c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 cao L\\u00e1ng H\\u00f2a L\\u1ea1c, n\\u1eb1m trong khu d\\u00e2n c\\u01b0 an ninh, \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 ti\\u1ec7n nghi, c\\u1ea7u thang m\\u00e1y, c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ed7 \\u0111\\u1ec3 oto c\\u1ea1nh t\\u00f2a nh\\u00e0 ho\\u1eb7c g\\u1eedi t\\u1ea1i Chung c\\u01b0 Phenikaa c\\u00e1ch 3 ph\\u00fat \\u0111i b\\u1ed9, c\\u00f3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi lau d\\u1ecdn v\\u1ec7 sinh khu v\\u1ef1c chung \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3.<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><figu